thanks msfenmore for putting these up everyday,
thank you for letting us know about Jeanne Cooper Katherine I knew she was very ill. she was a wonderful actor, and it is with a heavy heart that I say I will miss her a lot. May she rest in Peace
Thank you from Australia, Ms Fenmore
Thank you for the eps and for letting us know about Jeanne Cooper passing away. A wonderful lady & actress. RIP Jeanne Cooper. Y&R won't be the same without her.
Thank you, MsFenmore. Sad news- I cried when I heard about this. We will miss her.
